<L>__{exterior carriers' line day}
<A>__{the postman, chubby, ponytail and old george and all the carriers have taken positions. the postman sights through a telescope. he scans further down the line then stops when he sees ford. bloody, beaten within inches of his life. he's shackled surrounded by holnist guards. the postman's eyes turn to stone.}
<C>__{the postman}
<P>__{(to carriers)}
<D>__{stay here. no one moves until i give the orders.}
<A>__{he clicks his horse forward, toward the holnist line.}
